### EF Core Extensions - WhereBulkContains (GET)
GET {{host}}/products/where-bulk-contains

### EF Core Extensions - WhereBulkNotContains (GET)
GET {{host}}/products/where-bulk-not-contains

### EF Core Extensions - BulkRead (POST)
POST {{host}}/products/bulk-read
Content-Type: application/json

[
  { "id": 1, "productCode": "SKU-0001", "supplierCode": "SUP-001" },
  { "id": 2, "productCode": "SKU-0002", "supplierCode": "SUP-001" },
  { "id": 999999, "productCode": "SKU-NOT-EXIST", "supplierCode": "SUP-XXX" }
]

### EF Core Extensions - WhereBulkContainsFilterList (POST) - Existing items from list
POST {{host}}/products/filter-list/existing
Content-Type: application/json

[
  { "id": 3, "productCode": "SKU-0003", "supplierCode": "SUP-002" },
  { "id": 4, "productCode": "SKU-0004", "supplierCode": "SUP-002" },
  { "id": 888888, "productCode": "SKU-NOT-EXIST", "supplierCode": "SUP-YYY" }
]

### EF Core Extensions - WhereBulkNotContainsFilterList (POST) - Not existing items from list
POST {{host}}/products/filter-list/not-existing
Content-Type: application/json

[
  { "id": 5, "productCode": "SKU-0005", "supplierCode": "SUP-003" },
  { "id": 6, "productCode": "SKU-0006", "supplierCode": "SUP-003" },
  { "id": 777777, "productCode": "SKU-NOT-EXIST", "supplierCode": "SUP-ZZZ" }
]
